概率。\n    70\t\n    71\t#### 验收标准\n    72\t> 以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用
例详见 `tests/bdd/profile.feature`。\n    73\t\n    74\t```gherkin\n    75\tFeat
ure: Photo Upload\n    76\t  Scenario: User uploads avatar successfully\n    77\
