        text='## Comprehensive Matching Module Implementation Review\n\n---\n\n#
## 1. Backend (NestJS)\n\n#### Module Registration\n**File:** `apps/api/src/app.
module.ts`\n- `MatchingModule` is imported and registered alongside `AuthModule`
, `ProfileModule`, `BlocksModule`, etc.\n- TypeORM is configured with `autoLoadE
ntities: true` and `synchronize: false`.\n\n**File:** `apps/api/src/modules/matc
hing/matching.module.ts`\n- Imports `TypeOrmModule.forFeature([MatchActionEntity
, MatchEntity, UserProfileEntity, UserEntity, BlockEntity])`.\n- Providers: `Mat
chingService`, `MatchingGateway`.\n- Exports both service and gateway.\n\n#### C
ontroller & Endpoints\n**File:** `apps/api/src/modules/matching/matching.control
ler.ts`\n- `GET /matching/recommendations` — Returns recommendation cards with m
ode (`nearby`/`city`/`nationwide`) and limit.\n- `POST /matching/actions` — Reco
rds swipe action (`like`/`pass`/`super_like`). On mutual like, emits real-time m
atch event via `MatchingGateway`.\n- `GET /matches` — Returns paginated match li
st with cursor-based pagination.\n- All endpoints protected by `JwtAuthGuard`.\n
\n#### Service Logic\n**File:** `apps/api/src/modules/matching/matching.service.
ts`\n- **Recommendations:** Redis-cached (5 min TTL) with distributed lock patte
rn. Falls back to raw SQL query using haversine distance, composite scoring (dis
tance proximity 50%, recency 30%, new user boost 20%). Filters out already-swipe
d, matched, and blocked users. Returns empty if profile incomplete or missing lo
cation.\n- **Swipe Action:** Idempotent via duplicate-key exception handling. Cl
ears all mode caches on action. On `like`, checks for mutual like and creates ma
tch + conversation + participants in a TypeORM transaction.\n- **Match List:** C
ursor-based pagination using `created_at` DESC. Joins users and enriches with pr
ofile/conversation data.\n- **Match Summary:** Helper for gateway payload enrich
ment.\n\n#### WebSocket Gateway\n**File:** `apps/api/src/modules/matching/matchi
ng.gateway.ts`\n- Namespace: `matching`.\n- Joins/leaves rooms by `userId` from 
query param.\n- `emitMatchCreated()` broadcasts `match:created` event to both us
ers.\n- **No JWT authentication** on socket connections.\n\n#### DTOs\n**Files:*
* `apps/api/src/modules/matching/dto/`\n- `RecommendationQueryDto` — mode (`near
by`/`city`/`nationwide`), limit (1-50, default 20).\n- `RecommendationResponseDt
o` — `user_id`, `nickname`, `age`, `distance`, `bio`, `avatar_url`.\n- `SwipeAct
ionDto` — `target_id`, `action` (`like`/`pass`/`super_like`).\n- `MatchListRespo
nseDto` — `match_id`, `conversation_id`, `user_id`, `nickname`, `avatar_url`, `m
atched_at`.\n\n#### TypeORM Entities\n**Files:**\n- `apps/api/src/database/entit
ies/match-action.entity.ts` — `actor_id`, `target_id`, `action`, unique index on
`(actor_id, target_id)`.\n- `apps/api/src/database/entities/match.entity.ts` — `
user_a_id`, `user_b_id`, `status` (default `matched`), soft deletes via `deleted
_at`.\n- `apps/api/src/database/entities/conversation.entity.ts` — `match_id` (n
ullable), soft deletes.\n- `apps/api/src/database/entities/conversation-particip
ant.entity.ts` — `conversation_id`, `user_id`, `last_read_message_id`, unique on
`(conversation_id, user_id)`.\n- `apps/api/src/modules/blocks/block.entity.ts` —
`blocker_id`, `blocked_id`, `reason`.\n\n#### Migrations\n**File:** `apps/api/sr
c/database/migrations/20250410000000-InitialSchema.ts`\n- Creates all tables: `u
sers`, `user_profiles`, `user_photos`, `match_actions`, `matches`, `conversation
s`, `conversation_participants`, `messages`, `blocks`, `reports`.\n- Proper fore
ign keys, indexes, and unique constraints.\n- **No separate migration** for matc
hing-specific schema changes; everything is in the initial schema.\n\n---\n\n###
2. Mobile (Flutter)\n\n#### BLoC / Cubit Layer\n**Files:** `apps/mobile/lib/pres
entation/blocs/matching/`\n- `matching_bloc.dart` — Handles `RecommendationsRequ
ested`, `SwipeActionSubmitted`, `MatchModalDismissed`, `ExternalMatchReceived`. 
Emits states: `MatchingLoadInProgress`, `MatchingLoadSuccess`, `MatchingLoadEmpt
y`, `MatchingSwipeInProgress`, `MatchingMatchCreated`, `MatchingFailure`.\n- `ma
tch_list_cubit.dart` — Handles `fetchMatches()` with cursor pagination. Emits `M
atchListLoadInProgress`, `MatchListLoadSuccess`, `MatchListLoadFailure`.\n\n####
Pages\n**File:** `apps/mobile/lib/presentation/pages/home_page.dart`\n- Mode tab
s: 附近 / 同城 / 全国.\n- Gesture-based swipe card with drag threshold (120px), 
rotation, and LIKE/PASS badge overlays.\n- Action buttons (Pass / Like) at botto
m.\n- Integrates `MatchSuccessDialog` on `MatchingMatchCreated`.\n- Hardcoded Ch
inese UI strings.\n\n**File:** `apps/mobile/lib/presentation/pages/match_list_pa
ge.dart`\n- AppBar title "消息".\n- Empty state with illustration and CTA.\n- `L
istView.separated` with infinite scroll (triggers next page at end).\n- Each row
uses `MatchListItem`.\n\n#### Repository Layer\n**File:** `apps/mobile/lib/domai
n/repositories/matching_repository.dart`\n- Abstract contract with 3 methods: `g
etRecommendations`, `recordSwipeAction`, `getMatches`.\n\n**File:** `apps/mobile
/lib/data/repositories/matching_repository_impl.dart`\n- Direct Dio integration;
**does NOT use generated OpenAPI models**. Returns raw `List<Map<String, dynamic
>>` / `Map<String, dynamic>`.\n- Endpoints hit: `/matching/recommendations`, `/m
atching/actions`, `/matches`.\n\n#### DI Registration\n**File:** `apps/mobile/li
b/core/di/di.dart`\n- `MatchingRepository` → `MatchingRepositoryImpl`.\n- `Match
ingBloc` and `MatchListCubit` registered as factories.\n\n---\n\n### 3. Design S
ystem\n\n**File:** `packages/design-system/lib/src/molecules/swipe_card.dart`\n-
