- Supports `offsetX`, `rotation`, `showLikeBadge`, `showPassBadge`.\n- Semantics
identifiers per card.\n\n**File:** `packages/design-system/lib/src/organisms/swi
pe_card_stack.dart`\n- Renders up to 3 cards with depth effect (scale 0.95 / 0.9
