lib/src/molecules/match_list_item.dart`\n- Row with `SwAvatar`, nickname, `match
edAt`, chevron.\n\n**File:** `packages/design-system/lib/src/atoms/sw_action_but
ton.dart`\n- Circular like/pass buttons with semantics identifiers.\n\n---\n\n##
# 4. Tests\n\n#### Backend Service Tests\n**File:** `apps/api/src/modules/matchi
ng/tests/matching.service.spec.ts`\n- Covers: empty recommendations for incomple
te profile, cache hit, DB query + cache on miss, self-swipe rejection, pass acti
on, idempotent duplicate swipe, mutual like match creation, paginated match list
.\n- Mocks Redis, all repositories, and `DataSource`.\n\n#### Mobile BLoC Tests\
n**File:** `apps/mobile/test/presentation/blocs/matching_bloc_test.dart`\n- Cove
rs: fetch recommendations → `LoadSuccess`, empty recommendations → `LoadEmpty`, 
pass action → `SwipeInProgress` → `LoadSuccess`/`LoadEmpty`.\n- Uses `mocktail`.
\n- **No tests** for: match creation flow, `ExternalMatchReceived`, `MatchModalD
ismissed`, error recovery.\n\n#### Design System Golden Tests\n**File:** `packag
es/design-system/test/design_system_golden_test.dart`\n- Golden tests exist only
for `SwButton` variants and `SwTextField` variants.\n- **No golden tests** for `
SwipeCard`, `SwipeCardStack`, `MatchSuccessDialog`, `MatchListItem`, or `SwActio
nButton`.\n\n#### BDD Feature File\n**File:** `tests/bdd/matching.feature`\n- 9 
scenarios covering recommendations, caching, like/pass, duplicate idempotency, s
elf-swipe rejection, mutual match + conversation + Socket.IO, one-way pending, m
atch list.\n- Referenced by Maestro flows via `@syncWith` tags.\n\n---\n\n### 5.
API Contracts\n\n**File:** `docs/api-contracts/matching.yaml`\n- Defines `Recomm
endationCard` and `SwipeActionRequest` schemas.\n- **Gaps / Inconsistencies:**\n
 - Paths prefixed with `/api/v1/` but actual backend controller has no version p
refix.\n  - `GET /matching/recommendations` response schema shows `data.items` (
array wrapped in object), but actual controller returns `data` as a direct array
.\n  - `SwipeActionRequest.action` enum is `[like, pass, superlike]` but backend
DTO accepts `super_like` (underscore).\n  - Missing `GET /matches` endpoint enti
rely from contract.\n  - `superlike` vs `super_like` mismatch between contract a
nd backend.\n\n**File:** `docs/api-contracts/common.yaml`\n- Standard `ApiRespon
se`, `Pagination`, `ErrorResponse` schemas.\n\n---\n\n### 6. E2E (Maestro)\n\n**
Files:** `.maestro/flows/matching/`\n- `swipe_recommendations.yaml` — Launches a
pp, logs in, asserts tabs, switches modes, taps pass button. Does not verify car
d disappearance or mutual match.\n- `view_match_list.yaml` — Navigates to 消息 t
ab, asserts empty state text.\n\n---\n\n### 7. Guards\n\n**File:** `apps/api/src
/common/guards/jwt-auth.guard.ts`\n- Validates Bearer token, checks JWT signatur
e and `type === "access"`, verifies token is not blacklisted in Redis.\n- Applie
d to all matching controller endpoints.\n\n**File:** `apps/api/src/common/guards
/profile-completion.guard.ts`\n- Checks `UserProfileEntity.is_complete`. Throws 
`BusinessException(1000, "Profile incomplete...")` if incomplete.\n- **Exists bu
t is NOT applied** to any matching endpoint. The service does return empty recom
mendations for incomplete profiles, but the guard is unused.\n\n---\n\n## Consol
idated Gap Analysis\n\n| Category | Gap | Severity |\n|---|---|---|\n| **API Con
tract Accuracy** | Path prefix `/api/v1/` mismatch with actual routes; `data.ite
ms` vs direct array mismatch; `superlike` vs `super_like` enum mismatch; missing
`GET /matches` | High |\n| **Mobile ↔ Backend Sync** | Mobile `SwipeAction` enum
only has `like`/`pass` — cannot send `super_like` even though backend accepts it
| Medium |\n| **Real-time Notifications** | `socket_io_client` is in `pubspec.ya
ml` but mobile has **zero integration** for Socket.IO; `ExternalMatchReceived` e
vent exists in BLoC but is never triggered | High |\n| **Auth / Guards** | `Prof
ileCompletionGuard` is defined but **not applied** to matching endpoints; WebSoc
ket gateway has **no JWT auth** | High |\n| **Testing** | No `MatchListCubit` te
sts; mobile BLoC tests don\'t cover match creation or external match; no golden 
