cenario, no verification that swiped card disappears, no chat navigation | Mediu
m |\n| **Caching Edge Cases** | Redis cache is cleared on any swipe, but only fo
r the actor. If User B likes User A, User A\'s cache is not invalidated. | Low |
\n| **Pagination** | Match list uses `created_at` cursor but does not include ti
mezone handling concerns; no pagination tests for edge cases (duplicate cursors)
| Low |\n\n---\n\n### Summary\nThe matching module has a **solid backend foundat
ion** with proper database design, transactions, caching, and scoring logic. The
